data.description: Calling all dreamers, DIY enthusiasts, and nature lovers! This charming home with a new metal roof at 13654 RS Ave E in Scotts, MI, is your blank canvas for a tranquil escape. Nestled on six sprawling acres, this two-bedroom, two-bathroom home offers endless possibilities to create your own slice of paradise. With a little TLC, this home can be transformed. The sellers are leaving many of the materials to finish the projects, so with a little time and energy you can gain equity and create your own picture-perfect country home.
